   <body>
      <note type="warning">
         <p>In the event of a tipover, the risk of serious injury or death will be reduced if the
        operator is using the operator restraint system and follows the instructions provided.</p>
      </note>
      <fig>
         <image href="media/image84.png" placement="inline"/>
      </fig>
      <p>Always use operator restraint system.<fig>
            <image href="media/image85.png" placement="inline"/>
         </fig>
      </p>
      <p>Don’t jump.<fig>
            <image href="media/image86.png" placement="inline"/>
         </fig>
      </p>
      <p>Hold on tight.<fig>
            <image href="media/image87.png" placement="inline"/>
         </fig>
      </p>
      <p>Brace your feet and keep them within the operator’s
              compartment.<fig>
            <image href="media/image88.png" placement="inline"/>
         </fig>
      </p>
      <p>Lean away from the direction of fall.<fig>
            <image href="media/image89.png" placement="inline"/>
         </fig>
      </p>
      <p>Lean forward.</p>
